1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,040
Wait, did I just say that out loud?

2
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:06,080
Better just type it and pretend it was a typo.

3
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:09,119
Just keep typing. Don't look up.

4
00:00:09,119 --> 00:00:12,169
Eyes on the prize. Or at least the screen.

5
00:00:12,169 --> 00:00:15,210
Typing like my life depends on it.

6
00:00:15,210 --> 00:00:18,250
Now, where did all those keys go?
